column2: Aapki Yaad Aati Rahi Raat Bhar
Mere Mehboob Na Ja Aaj Ki Raat
Tere Bin Soona Mere Mann Ka Mandir
Dil Ke Arman Ansuon Mein Bah Gaye
Yeh Hawa Yeh Fiza Aa Bhi Ja
Chale Ja Chale Ja Jahan Pyar Miley
Aaja Meri Barbad Mohabbat Ke Sahare
Socha Tha Kya Kya Ho Gaya
Ae Zamane Tu Kar Le Sitam Pe Sitam
Tum Ko Mere Dil Ne Pukara
Ameeron Ki Sham Gharibon Ke Naam
Duniya Mein Tera Hai Bada Naam
Mohabbat Ab Tijarat Ban Gai Hai
O Mere Majhi Mere Sajan Hai
Raat Ne Kya Kya Khwab Dikhaye
Main Teri Nazar Ka Suroor Hoon
Teri Ankh Ke Ansoo Pee Jaoon

Waqt Ne Kiya Kya Haseen Sitam

Teri Duniya Mein Dil Lagta Nahin

Dost Dost Na Raha Pyar Pyar Na Raha

Jis Dil Mein Basa Tha Pyar Tera

Kabhi Na Kabhi Kahin Na Kahin

Man Re Tu Kahe Na Dheer Dhare
Mile Na Phool To Kanton Se Dosti
Main Yeh Sochkar Uske Dar Se Utha
Maut Kabhi Bhi Mil Sakti Hai
Ae Mere Dil Yahan Tu Akela
Falsafa Pyar Ka Tum Kya Jano
Yaad Na Jaye Beete Dinon Ki
Yeh Ansoo Mere Dil Ki Zuban Hai
Chale Aaj Tum Jahan Se (O Door Ke Musafir)
Koi Sagar Dil Ko Bahlata Nahin
Hui Sham Unka Khayal Aa Gaya
Nafrat Ki Duniya Ko Chhod Ke
Kahaniyan Sunati Hai Pawan Aati Jaati
Mera Dushman Tu Meri Dosti Ko Tarse
Mujhe Mat Roko Mujhe Gaane Do
Kya Se Kya Ho Gaya Bewafa
Apni To Har Aah Ek Toofan Hai
Hum Bekhudi Mein Tum Ko Pukare
Garibon Ki Suno Woh Tumhari Sunega
Uljhan Suljhe Na Rasta Sujhe Na
Yehi Woh Jaga Hai Yehi Woh Fazayen

Raat Bhar Ka Hai Mehman Andhera
Koi Lauta De Mere Beete Huye Din
Panthi Hoon Main Us Path Ka
Teri Duniya Se Hoke Majboor Chala
Agar Sun Le To Ek Naghma
Ghunghroo Ki Tarah Bajta Hi Raha
Agar Dil Hamara Sheeshe Ke Badle
Yeh Lal Rang Kab Mujhe Chhodega
Ek Hasina Thi Ek Deewana Tha
Chhup Gaya Koi Re Door Se Pukar Ke
Dil Ka Khilauna Hay Toot Gaya
Guzra Hua Zamana Aata Nahin (Hafiz Khuda Tumhara)
Haye Re Woh Din Kyon Na Aaye
Woh Bhooli Dastan Lo Phir Yaad
Aap Kyon Roye (Jo Hamne Dastan Apni)
Chain Nahin Aaye Kahan Dil Jaye
Hai Isi Mein Pyar Ki Abroo
Main To Tum Sang Nain Milake
Woh Dekho Jala Ghar Kisi Ka
Ja Re Ja Re Ud Ja Re Panchhi
Rehte The Kabhi Jinke Dil Mein Ham

Aaj Kal Mein Dhal Gaya Din

Tum Humse Mile Hum Tumse Mile

Yeh Raat Bhi Ja Rahi Hai
Zamane Mein Aji Aise Koi Nadan Hota

Tum Mujhse Door Chale Jana Na

Jeet Hi Lenge Baazi Hum Tum

Yaad Mein Teri Jaag Jaag Ke Hum
Ye Dil Tum Bin Lagta Nahin
